Package com.bonitasoft.test.toolkit.model

Interface ProcessDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Callable<ProcessDefinition>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProcessDefinitionProxy
    public interface ProcessDefinition
extends Callable<ProcessDefinition>
    Represent a Bonita process definition. It is the entry point to start new process instances. A ProcessDefinition can be retrieved using the BonitaTestToolkit.getProcessDefinition(String): 
     @Test
 void test_my_process(BonitaTestToolkit toolkit) {
     ProcessDefinition myProcess = toolkit.getProcessDefinition("myProcess");
     ...
 }
